data.description: Beautiful east facing fully remodeled home in the Lambert High School district! New kitchen cabinets and granite countertops installed one week ago! The following also are all BRAND NEW: new convection gas range with wifi and airfryer (install 12/9/23), New dishwasher(12/9/23), New bathroom faucets, New shower faucet fixtures, New light fixtures, New carpet and pad, New luxury vinyl plank wood flooring in dining/living/den/bathrooms/laundry, new ceiling fans, new paint on ceilings/walls/baseboards/doors/etc, custom paint on cabinets with matching storage piece in kitchen. Large private cul-de-sac with HUGE backyard. loft/ playroom. Roof new in 2020. Heat pumps new in 2020; New exterior paint 2020. Large walk-in master closet. Large walk-in pantry. Kitchen has space for a table along with a formal dining room. Donat miss this treasure!
